not some little [BLEEP] minnow.

07:19.967 --> 07:22.767
If you're gonna make a whale,
baby, ya gotta go big!

07:22.867 --> 07:24.300
And I mean big, big!

07:24.400 --> 07:27.233
We appreciate your spirit,
ma'am, but this is about...

07:27.333 --> 07:29.667
