think we need to be trying--

07:41.700 --> 07:42.800
Let's do it!

07:42.900 --> 07:44.433
Let's do it!
Let's band together!

07:44.533 --> 07:48.067
She's right, if we all band
together, we can pull this off!

07:48.100 --> 07:51.133
What do you say? Who's with me?
You? You?

07:51.233 --> 07:53.200
Yeah! Yeah!
The good guy's with us.

07:53.300 --> 07:54.500
Let's do it!

07:54.600 --> 07:58.200
( MUSIC PLAYING )

08:15.933 --> 08:17.733
