a dive for the King.

09:14.800 --> 09:17.733
How could I ever trust
you again?

09:17.833 --> 09:22.467
What? I trust you!

09:23.767 --> 09:26.300
Trust fall, hm?

09:29.533 --> 09:31.400
Goodbye, Starman.

09:37.667 --> 09:39.533
Oh, no.

09:39.633 --> 09:42.500
You'll pay for this,
Vernon Brown.

09:44.800 --> 09:46.600
Hey, ma? Can I talk to you
for a second?

09:46.700 --> 09:48.300
What's up?

09:48.400 --> 09:51.067
Hey, I'm really glad you decided
to stick around and help out.

09:51.100 --> 09:53.500
And Charlotte really seems to
be having fun with you.

09:53.600 --> 09:55.367
She's a helluva girl.

09:55.467 --> 09:57.700
Ah, good job, everybody!

09:57.800 --> 10:00.033
We are definitely gonna win
it this time!

10:00.133 --> 10:01.867
